<header class="page-header">
  <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Personal</p>
  <h1 class="page-header__title">Saved passages</h1>
  <p class="page-header__subtitle">
    Lines you marked while reading — with room for a private note.
  </p>
</header>

<p class="section-intro saved-passages__notice">
  Saved passages live in this browser only. Clearing site data removes them.
  Export a Markdown file to back up or move to another device.
</p>

<div class="saved-passages__toolbar">
  <button type="button" class="saved-passages__btn" id="saved-passages-export">Export Markdown</button>
  <label class="saved-passages__btn saved-passages__btn--file">
    Import Markdown
    <input type="file" id="saved-passages-import" accept=".md,text/markdown,text/plain" hidden>
  </label>
  <p id="saved-passages-status" class="saved-passages__status" hidden></p>
</div>

<div id="saved-passages-root" class="saved-passages-page" aria-live="polite"></div>
